{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8ffeb7c1-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2718"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2718"},"text":"§ 2718.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Fees received for use of Blair House","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id8ffeb7c2-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2718/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Use of fees","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding any other provision of law, funds received by the Department of State in connection with use of Blair House (including reimbursements and surcharges for services and goods provided and fees for use of Blair House facilities) may be credited to the appropriate appropriation account of the Department of State which is currently available. Such funds shall be available only for maintenance and other expenses of Blair House.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id8ffeb7c3-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2718/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Compliance with Budget Act","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The authority of this section may be exercised only to such extent or in such amounts as are provided in advance in an appropriation Act.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8ffeb7c4-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1956-08-01/ch841"},"text":"Aug. 1, 1956, ch. 841","children":[],"tail":", title I, § 46, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/246/tI/s119/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–246, title I, § 119(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-02-16"},"text":"Feb. 16, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/26"},"text":"104 Stat. 26","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/138/tI/s123"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–138, title I, § 123","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/659"},"text":"105 Stat. 659","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id8ffeb7c5-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id8ffeb7c6-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id8ffeb7c7-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Budget Act, referred to in subsec. (b) heading, probably means the Congressional Budget Act of 1974, titles I through IX of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/344"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–344","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-07-12"},"text":"July 12, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/297"},"text":"88 Stat. 297","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s621"},"text":"section 621 of Title 2","children":[],"tail":", The Congress, and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id8ffeb7c8-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 46 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1956-08-01"},"text":"Aug. 1, 1956","children":[],"tail":", was renumbered section 47 by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/246/s119/1"},"text":"section 119(1) of Pub. L. 101–246","children":[],"tail":", and subsequently renumbered, and set out as a Short Title of 1956 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2651"},"text":"section 2651 of this title","children":[],"tail":", prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/138/tI/s111/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–138, title I, § 111(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/654"},"text":"105 Stat. 654","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id8ffeb7c9-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1991—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/138"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–138","children":[],"tail":" struck out “for the fiscal years 1990 and 1991,” after “provision of law,”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
